--- !u!114 &1284606562
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1284606559}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b149de7df7147e74a934894c5da5617d, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  conversation:
  - speakerName: 'Nikola Tesla:'
    sentence: Please don't hurt me, stranger! I've already lost everything.
  - speakerName: '    Player:'
    sentence: You're in pretty bad shape. I don't know what happened to you, and
      I don't care. I'm just searching for my own self.
  - speakerName: 'Nikola Tesla:'
    sentence: You fell here and you don't remember anything, do you? Because you're
      one of the losers too.
  - speakerName: '     Player:'
    sentence: What does that mean? I'm the strongest in the world and I've never
      lost. Anyway, I really don't remember how I came to this new world with a shadow
      body.
  - speakerName: 'Nikola Tesla:'
    sentence: This world is called Araf. This is where we losers forget our own selves.
      I'm Nikola Tesla. Since I was very intelligent in my other life, I easily figured
      this place out.
  - speakerName: 'Nikola Tesla:'
    sentence: But just like in my previous life, I'm weak. I lost to Thomas Edison.
      He was jealous of me and had me killed in a hotel room.
  - speakerName: '      Player:'
    sentence: If he's jealous of you, you're stronger than him.
  - speakerName: 'Nikola Tesla:'
    sentence: I was the best at science. I could even help you find yourself, but
      in return, take my revenge!
  - speakerName: 'Nikola Tesla:'
    sentence: You have to beat me before I can trust you. As a reward, I will give
      you electric power.
  - speakerName: '      Player:'
    sentence: Deal!
  bossToWakeUp: {fileID: 0}
